author: rbhattacharya04
body: Inclusion of 2 new trigger bits in the custom Muon POG nanoAOD, for the usage of Muon POG. The previous section, created to include the trigger bits for the usage of Muon POG, is completely exhausted. Needed to create another section to include the new triggers.
title: 2 New Trigger bits for Muon POG NanoAOD
